    <div class="p-5">
        <h1 class="text-center fs-1">Fanatec</h1>
        <hr />
        <p class="text-decoration-underline">Fanatec: High-End Sim Racing Hardware</p>
        <p>Fanatec is a premium brand known for producing high-performance sim racing hardware, catering to both casual enthusiasts and professional eSports racers. Founded in 1997 by Thomas Jackermeier and operated by Endor AG, a German company, Fanatec has become a respected name in the world of racing simulation.</p>
        <hr />
        <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5 mb-4 fs-1">Product Range</h2>
        <p>
            Fanatec offers a wide range of sim racing products, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li class="mb-5">Steering Wheels: High-quality, realistic wheels modeled after real motorsport designs. Options range from Formula-style wheels to GT and rally-inspired variants.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Wheel Bases: The motorized units that power the wheels, featuring Direct Drive or belt-driven force feedback for an immersive racing feel.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Pedals: Load-cell and Hall-effect sensor pedals that provide precise control over braking, throttle, and clutch inputs.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Shifters and Handbrakes: Add-ons like the ClubSport Shifter SQ and ClubSport Handbrake offer even more realism for manual transmission and rally racing fans.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Cockpits and Accessories: Mounting solutions and rigs designed for stability and adjustability.</li>
        </ul>
        <hr />
        <p class="fw-bold">
            Key Features and Technologies
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li class="mb-5">Direct Drive Technology: Fanatec’s Podium Series uses direct drive motors for maximum force feedback detail and strength.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Modularity: Many components are interchangeable and customizable, allowing users to build a rig that suits their exact preferences.</li>
            <li class="mb-5">Cross-Platform Support: Fanatec products are compatible with PC, PlayStation, and Xbox, though specific products may be platform-locked.</li>
        </ul>
        <hr />
        <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5 mb-4 fs-1">Target Audience</h2>
        <p>
            Fanatec targets a wide audience, from hobbyist sim racers to professional eSports drivers. Its products strike a balance between enthusiast-grade quality and consumer accessibility, often providing more advanced features at a better value compared to competitors.
        </p>
        <hr />
        <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5 mb-4 fs-1">Community and Reputation</h2>
        <p>
            Fanatec has built a loyal community thanks to its high standards of build quality, realism, and performance. However, some users have noted issues with customer support and product availability, especially during high demand periods. Still, the brand remains one of the top choices for serious sim racers.
        </p>
